  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "hFXmMmG1UQU+NCBBWchs7VEDqAgIsFRiFibUOLGAnGs=",
    "originContent": "- **Token-level dynamic scheduling**: Add new requests mid-generation without waiting for batch completion",
