    "rowsha": "8Sv098O9vQ+KoQ3L867VQSIn+U84L+g+LpoVX2ngILw=",
    "originContent": "- **Two-phase scheduler**: Seamlessly continue running requests while admitting new ones",
    "translatedContent": "- **两阶段调度器**：无缝继续运行请求，同时接收新请求"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "wvtD/VqvfUGEwyXVI1212NKohDuEXv9EyER2nKLBddg=",
    "originContent": "- **Request state tracking**: Precise `num_computed_tokens` management for efficient resume",
    "translatedContent": "- **请求状态跟踪**：精确管理 `num_computed_tokens`，高效恢复"
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "Dx/wz7v0YUOYWjOGLqyfdllwpwJA1mTwOa4VWcnp4O8=",
