  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "smGzJQl0mcsFy82taL2KGYTIwobm+WQmAIPl9qA44oY=",
    "originContent": "### INT8 Quantization",
    "translatedContent": "### INT8 量化"
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "A2KSz0k8gaVQMc6rmiVJyopN7Uj45V/xmlaoW71DnHY=",
    "originContent": "- **Group-wise quantization**: Configurable group size (32, 64, 128)",
    "translatedContent": "- **分组量化**：可配置分组大小（32、64、128）"
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "refNpgDRCf9XRgXqFtgk8iHjPBa8Qo452gj6zQFcPZA=",
    "originContent": "- **cuBLASLt integration**: Hardware-accelerated INT8 GEMM",
    "translatedContent": "- **cuBLASLt 集成**：硬件加速的 INT8 GEMM"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "VupejMCrKhgrk6YhChVr9Yr8BXYAvV794H9LUyA6e5I=",
    "originContent": "- **Minimal accuracy loss**: < 1% perplexity degradation on Llama models",
    "translatedContent": "- **极小的精度损失**：Llama模型上困惑度下降 < 1%"
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "hZiOdKxxJZqJ+t6B6nhGhO5VvT/mw9Klir9DoEIRAU4=",
    "originContent": "### Paged Attention",
    "translatedContent": "### 分页注意力"
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "IpORQNrhsNAjmQV0iTbH2x/FlVT1ZMlrC5kpAa5JXfQ=",
    "originContent": "- **Block-level KV cache**: Efficient memory allocation without fragmentation",
    "translatedContent": "- **块级 KV 缓存**：高效内存分配，无碎片"
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "KCC1sKe81N6Ef9UhJHghC/+wRqrMGCmd+PHtwQFUZ80=",
    "originContent": "- **Dynamic sequence management**: Per-sequence cache offsets for flexible scheduling",
    "translatedContent": "- **动态序列管理**：每序列缓存偏移，实现灵活调度"
  },
  {
    "row": 136,
    "rowsha": "4vSpJ8stWfPnSFTZkM0IOvNOCJqKnvNufqdsdulDvUo=",
    "originContent": "- **Batched cache operations**: Single kernel for multi-sequence K/V writes",
    "translatedContent": "- **批处理缓存操作**：单核函数支持多序列 K/V 写入"
  },
  {
    "row": 137,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 138,
    "rowsha": "2nQVFtz1sZjmOCce3nfkp5adYh8oisZ8/LttIC5jik0=",
    "originContent": "### Continuous Batching Scheduler",
    "translatedContent": "### 连续批处理调度器"
  },
  {
    "row": 139,
    "rowsha": "2B/ZMrRReGwoOUFzO0gtvKvG7LuGbM7RuaSArNYLZFw=",
    "originContent": "- **Two-phase scheduling**:",
    "translatedContent": "- **两阶段调度**："
  },
  {
    "row": 140,
    "rowsha": "5vsj9UyqTI5ECDXPlMTwXCgruGlUEa9r/V3B/9ST/9w=",
    "originContent": "  1. **Phase 1**: Continue all RUNNING requests (no interruption)",
    "translatedContent": "  1. **阶段1**：继续所有运行中的请求（不打断）"
  },
  {
    "row": 141,
    "rowsha": "mUoT5wQiwHYwihYEj6y5Zv9qXYA4b6rQgRooCJcznAw=",
    "originContent": "  2. **Phase 2**: Admit WAITING requests to fill remaining capacity",
    "translatedContent": "  2. **阶段2**：接纳等待中的请求填充剩余容量"
  },
  {
    "row": 142,
    "rowsha": "UNNot9A5p+78BsrNl67JNL8YXKPMPLTt+0QrayuzPO4=",
    "originContent": "- **Request states**: WAITING → RUNNING → FINISHED (with PREEMPTED support)",
    "translatedContent": "- **请求状态**：等待 → 运行 → 完成（支持抢占）"
  },
  {
    "row": 143,
    "rowsha": "VWOEgDIEPCrxdQkSMssHTZ5e/GEdFPIQ7zfy1/E/Zyk=",
    "originContent": "- **Token-level granularity**: `num_computed_tokens` tracking for precise resume",
    "translatedContent": "- **令牌级粒度**：通过 `num_computed_tokens` 精确追踪恢复点"
  },
